---
title: Cheesy Stuffed Beyond Meat® Burgers with BBQ Oven-Baked Wedges
description: It's a double cheese-stuffed Beyond Meat® burger extravaganza! Cream cheese is mixed with sharp cheddar and hidden inside juicy Beyond Meat® burgers. These beauties are finished off with tomatoes and Dijonnaise, then served with BBQ-seasoned potato wedges for the very best burger dinner!

